text: Jorge Alvarez may refer to: *Jorge Álvarez (rower) (born 1959), Cuban Olympic rower *Jorge Montt Álvarez (1845–1922), vice-admiral of the Chilean navy and president of Chile from 1891 to 1896 *Jorge Álvares (died 1521), Portuguese explorer *Jorge Álvarez (music producer), Argentine music producer *Jorge Eduardo Álvarez (born 1990), Chilean footballer
title: Jorge Alvarez
